abstract: Elizabeth Warren, now running for a United States Senate seat in Massachusetts, is taking some credit for the Occupy Wall Street movement. She told Samuel P. Jacobs of The Daily Beast: "I created much of the intellectual foundation for what they do. I support what they do."
